{"tid":90241,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"健身一問","createTime":"2017-01-22T02:15:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-23T05:20:01.000Z","uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c6be844cdd1bd3fe304382cd78bbd1f21a5038b","tid":90241,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T02:15:14.000Z","msg":"小腿點先可以操得大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時都有操開腳 大脾成個東瓜咁大<br />\n其實小腿都唔算好幼但對比下好似好了瘦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be60f4c8c249f0737627d0168e83e8c807f1f5a0","tid":90241,"uid":47849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T19:11:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小腿點先可以操得大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n平時都有操開腳 大脾成個東瓜咁大<br />\n其實小腿都唔算好幼但對比下好似好了瘦咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n快跑/單車<br />\n爆發性嗰種<br />\n將力集中用係小腿<br />\n<br />\n你睇下足球員嘅小腿就知<br />\n<br />\n佢地平時操都係練腳嘅爆發性<br />\n跟足球員咁練"},{"pid":"83be2f763f760b970d0fd756f580aea04a3e9cd3","tid":90241,"uid":78643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T20:00:14.000Z","msg":"sitting/standing calf raises<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c862b2ac33e630a15978979fe0034226006f12f","tid":90241,"uid":6238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T20:05:27.000Z","msg":"This is evident when studies have assessed  bre type distribution across a number of di erent muscle groups. For example in the gluteus maximus has shown a slow twitch percentage of between 52 and 68%, the hamstrings between 43 and 67%, <span style=\"color: red;\">the gastrocnemius between 44 and 78% and the soleus of between 70 and 90%. </span>This not only highlights the variation in  bre type distributions within certain populations, but also that muscle groups such as the soleus, that are activated most often and in low demand activities such walking, have the need for higher fatigue resistance in the form of higher proportions of type 1  bres."},{"pid":"5df98f069ee912c343901ea9bdaab4ac77e141ba","tid":90241,"uid":3696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T03:25:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>sitting/standing calf raises<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n之前都有做過一排 但效果唔係好明顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n試下再操返先"},{"pid":"b9a01a02c8e273d824dff64238bc560f030758a2","tid":90241,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T05:20:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmTNy3V5TeYh62Pmx5G76pXvZQCYHS9GjqyQNicEcdeL2N?filename=cX8yd85.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcX8yd85.jpg&h=e1094d63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n跳繩👍🏻"}]}